    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single ASTM F1717 test configuration; this shortfall is accepted given the standardized regulatory test protocol and the scope of the COU. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level conclusion. FEA ensemble results satisfy pre-established acceptance bounds (E/uval <1.96, percent difference <10%) for all three primary QoIs across all three independent FEA implementations. Decision: Accepted.",
